<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><a href="https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-cn-1827/Si"><img src="https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--resized-images/scp-cn-1827/Si/medium.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="Si" class="image" /></a>
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>SCP-CN-1827的冠部标本。保存于Area-CN-07-δ。</p>
